हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: She was born into hardship, shaped by a cruel fate. But through every struggle, she rose—stronger, wiser, and unstoppable. Watch Stars in My Heart—a powerful story of resilience, dreams, and a woman who dares to shine.
